{"tid":2375626,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懲教署申請重建荔枝角收押所","createTime":"2021-01-22T07:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T07:25:04.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b12784c8667e5f8758dd240f6ea7c3f6480259ea","tid":2375626,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/131455797049356/posts/1563985913796330/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F131455797049356%2Fposts%2F1563985913796330%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4Tfpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=2dc45586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/131455797049356/posts/1563985913796330/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n由於近年收押所面對持續過度擠迫的情況，懲教署向城規會申請將荔枝角收押所重建為樓高13層的大樓，可容納810名羈留人士，比現時增加410個，同時提供更多探訪窗格、公務探訪室、醫療設施及更生設施。署方亦表示新監獄會引入經擴充的輔助數據中心，提升運作效率從而為羈留人士和懲教人員提供一個可持續和智能的監獄環境，解決目前平均每天使用率超過100%的情況。<br />\n<br />\n公眾可在2021年2月16日提出意見<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/A_K16_44.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Ftc%2Fplan_application%2FA_K16_44.html&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4Tfpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=0c2aa485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/A_K16_44.html</a>"},{"pid":"2c56f72f96d6cd523d3c34c1cb8c0ee745ca2204","tid":2375626,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:25:01.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"5f781fd2e97984037114f550f3b8348b595a84a7","tid":2375626,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:25:04.000Z","msg":"新疆集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}